title: Major internal improvements
message:
Major internal improvements

- Latest Gradle plugin
- Target API 26
- Minimum API 17
- Performance improvements on the song index screen
  - Parallel loading from disk for more throughput
  - Reduced memory usage by retaining only needed fields
  - Dropping loader and JSON parses from memory once done loading
  - Flattened view hierarchy
